In re Kavanagh’s Estate. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. October 24, 1890.) Accounting of the executors of Benjamin A. Kavanagh, deceased. See, also, 5 S. V. Supp. 676; 6 S. V. Supp. 669 ; 9 S. V. Supp. 443, 941; 10 S. Y. Supp. 899.

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

So opinion. Motion denied.
